-----------------------------------------------------

📍 GPS Neo-6M
VCC → 3.3V (ESP32)
GND → GND
TX  → GPIO4
RX  → (optional GPIO5)

📍 SOS Button
One leg → GPIO18
Other leg → GND
(Use INPUT_PULLUP)

📍 LED
Long leg → GPIO19 (via 220Ω resistor)
Short leg → GND

📍 Buzzer
+ → GPIO21
– → GND

-----------------------------------------------------

⚠ VERY IMPORTANT:
✔ All GND must be common
✔ MT3608 output must be exactly 4.0V
✔ Do NOT power ESP32 from MT3608
✔ ESP32 powered via USB / 5V regulated input
